# Hugging Face token for pyannote speaker diarization models
# Required for speaker diarization feature in WhisperX
#
# Setup steps:
# 1. Create account at https://huggingface.co
# 2. Accept terms at https://huggingface.co/pyannote/speaker-diarization-3.1
# 3. Accept terms at https://huggingface.co/pyannote/segmentation-3.0
# 4. Create token at https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
#
# Without this token, transcription will still work but speaker
# identification will be disabled.
HF_TOKEN=your_huggingface_token_here
